OL,3,C'Nothing doctors can do': MAFS dating
OL,4,Ccoach Mel Schilling says cancer has
OL,5,Cspread
OL,7,FMarried at First Sight dating coach
OL,8,FMel Schilling has said her cancer has
OL,9,Fspread to her brain and doctors have
OL,10,Ftold her there is "nothing further
OL,11,Fthey can do".
OL,13,FThe TV star, 54, was first diagnosed
OL,14,Fwith colon cancer in December 2023 and
OL,15,Fwent on to receive the all clear, but
OL,16,Fsmall nodules were later discovered in
OL,17,Fher lungs in February 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
