PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773450175
OL,3,C'Nothing doctors can do': MAFS dating
OL,4,Ccoach Mel Schilling says cancer has
OL,5,Cspread
OL,7,F"I honestly don't know how long I have
OL,8,Fleft, but I do know I will fight to my
OL,9,Flast breath and will be surrounded by
OL,10,Fthe love and support of my people,"
OL,11,FSchilling said.
OL,13,FShe thanked people for messaging her
OL,14,Fwords of encouragement and support and
OL,15,Fsaid they have helped "shape the
OL,16,Fmindset" she needed to "keep fighting".
