OL,3,C'Nothing doctors can do': MAFS dating
OL,4,Ccoach Mel Schilling says cancer has
OL,5,Cspread
OL,7,FChannel 4 said MAFS Australia expert
OL,8,FJohn Aiken will step in to replace
OL,9,FSchilling for the remainder of the UK
OL,10,Fseries, which is currently being
OL,11,Ffilmed.
OL,13,F"All of us at Channel 4 are
OL,14,Fimmeasurably saddened by the news
OL,15,Fabout Mel's health, and are sending
OL,16,Fall of our love and support to Mel and
OL,17,Fher family," the broadcaster said.
