OL,3,C'Nothing doctors can do': MAFS dating
OL,4,Ccoach Mel Schilling says cancer has
OL,5,Cspread
OL,7,F"Over five series of Married at First
OL,8,FSight UK, and twelve series of Married
OL,9,Fat First Sight Australia, Mel has
OL,10,Fbecome a hugely valued and much-loved
OL,11,Fpart of the Channel 4 family; to many
OL,12,Fof us she is a friend as well as a
OL,13,Fcolleague.
OL,15,F"Her wisdom, warmth, humour and
OL,16,Fkindness shine through, and these
OL,17,Fqualities mean that everyone involved
OL,18,Fin MAFS, from the producers and
OL,19,Fcontributors, to the viewers, love and
OL,20,Frespect her as much as we do.
