OL,7,F"MAFS UK is currently filming and,
OL,8,Fwith Mel's blessing, her good friend
OL,9,Fand fellow MAFS Australia expert, John
OL,10,FAiken, has done us the great favour of
OL,11,Fstepping in for her for this series."
